# This file is used in a custom pipeline for picking an assignee at random
# for template-update merge requests.
#
# REPOOWNERS is propagated to each service with every template-update, so for
# changes this file need to be changed only once.
#
# Assignees for template-update are picked based on the gitlab group, so
# these are the different prefixes.
#
# During verification (a pipeline step), this request needs to return
# exactly 1 result: https://gitlab.wearespindle.com/api/v4/users/?search={user}

